long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Token Holder Comparison Tool

Effortlessly compare token holder addresses across multiple tokens on Solana or EVMs. Input token contract addresses, find shared holders, and explore detailed address information with a clean, interactive interface. 

This tool simplifies identifying shared holders and provides navigation to external details with a single click. 

Perfect for blockchain analysts, developers, and enthusiasts who want insights into token holder overlaps in a streamlined side panel experience. 

Customize your API and get a guided tutorial right within the app. This app uses helius API! Etherscan API! Basescan API!
